Keep yourself and your loved ones safe from #COVID19 this holiday season!🎄 Stay home if you have symptoms. 

Common symptoms include:
⚫ Fever
⚫ Runny nose 
⚫ Persistent cough 
⚫ Sore throat 
⚫ Headache

🎁Give the gift of health this festive season. 

#DoItAll to protect people who are at higher risk of severe illness from #COVID19, such as the elderly.

Wash your hands, show you care this holiday season. 🎄

Don't forget to wash your 👐🏿 with soap🧼 & water💧 or an alcohol-based hand gel regularly. Help stop the spread of #COVID19 & other diseases.

Stay safe from #COVID19 this holiday season🎄, get #vaccinated .

Getting vaccinated helps prevent you from getting severely ill or dying from the virus.

I suspect #COVID19 took the person who composed the Christmas and New year messages we used to share in WhatsApp groups.
#Happy2022

➡️Over 60
